===Interjection===
'''"teh"'''
# a yelled cry by Link from Zelda: Ocarina of Time which represents the energy he is putting into his sword attack.  May be used by any person to make their sword attack more powerful.
# a statement of joy and/or slight randomness, because of less sword use in this world; for more emphasis this one syllable word may be accented at the end to make a rising accent, which makes it progressively louder. 
